WEBVTT

1
00:56:15.430 --> 00:56:17.060 
当他跑去康乃狄克、纽约、加州
When he goes to Connecticut, New York and California

2
00:56:17.140 --> 00:56:18.470 
他就会违反联邦法
he'll have violated federal law.

3
