哈佛学生手册
Harvard student handbook.

7
00:56:31.520 --> 00:56:32.850 
每位新生都有一本这个
Every freshman is issued one of this.

8
00:56:32.950 --> 00:56:33.920 
这里面有写
Somewhere in this book says...

9
00:56:33.990 --> 00:56:35.820 
不能窃取其它学生的东西
You can't steal from another student.

10
00:56:37.820 --> 00:56:38.760 
这就是我们需要的
This is what we needed.

11
00:56:38.820 --> 00:56:39.650 
我们去见桑默斯校长
We're going to Summers.

12
