你根本见不到桑默斯
You can't get a meeting with Larry Summers.

13
00:56:42.030 --> 00:56:43.520 
我哥和我，我们付了学费
My brother and I pay tuition at this school,

14
00:56:43.630 --> 00:56:45.430 
我们以高分进入本校
we carry a 3.9 GPA at this school,

15
